class="post-2709 page type-page status-publish has-post-thumbnail ast-article-single remove-featured-img-padding" id="post-2709" itemtype="https://schema.org/CreativeWork" itemscope="itemscope"><header class="entry-header ast-no-title ast-header-without-markup"></header><div class="entry-content clear"
 itemprop="text"><div data-elementor-type="wp-post" data-elementor-id="2709" class="elementor elementor-2709"><section class="elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-2af40a5 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default" data-id="2af40a5" data-element_type="section" data-e-type="section" id="homeheader"><div class="elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default"><div class="elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-2d4ac8e" data-id="2d4ac8e" data-element_type="column" data-e-type="column"><div class="elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated"><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-15aee6b elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="15aee6b" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default"><div class="elementor-widget-container"><h1>Bienvenido a Belleza para tod@s</h1><p>Belleza para tod@s te trae toda la información, novedades y noticias de belleza, maquillaje, cuidado personal, cuidado de la piel, cuidado del cabello, moda, estilo, tendencias, actualidad y demás temas relacionados.</p></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class="elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-ad4b33b elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default" data-id="ad4b33b" data-element_type="section" data-e-type="section"><div class="elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default"><div class="elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-3ec3f62" data-id="3ec3f62" data-element_type="column" data-e-type="column"><div class="elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated"><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-aee7f46 elementor-widget elementor-widget-jw-posts" data-id="aee7f46" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" id="homepagemainpost" data-settings="{&quot;columns&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;columns_tablet&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;columns_mobile&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}" data-widget_type="jw-posts.default"><div class="elementor-widget-container"><div class="elementor-jw-posts jet-widgets"><div class="jw-posts col-row  jw-equal-cols"><div class="jw-posts__item col-desk-1"><div class="jw-posts__inner-box"><div class="post-thumbnail"><a href="https://www.bellezaparatodos.com/2022/06/08/revolution-cocacola-creations/" class="post-thumbnail__link"><img fetchpriority="high" fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="post-thumbnail__img wp-post-image" src="https://static.bellezaparatodos.com/2022/06/Revolution-x-Coca-Cola-Creations-Collection-Post-Cover-Blog.jpg" alt="Colección Revolution x Coca-Cola Creations" width="1200" height="675"></a></div><div class="jw-posts__inner-content"><h4 class="entry-title"><a href="https://www.bellezaparatodos.com/2022/06/08/revolution-cocacola-creations/">Colección Revolution x Coca-Cola Creations</a></h4><div class="entry-excerpt">La colección Revolution x Coca-Cola Creations ha sido creada en colaboración con la compañía de Coca-Cola y esta inspirada en el nuevo sabor de edición limitada, Space.</div><div class="jw-more-wrap"><a href="https://www.bellezaparatodos.com/2022/06/08/revolution-cocacola-creations/" class="btn btn-primary elementor-button elementor-size-md jw-more"><span class="btn__text">Sigue leyendo</span></a></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-60c777a elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading" data-id="60c777a" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="heading.default"><div class="elementor-widget-container"><h2 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default"><a href="https://www.bellezaparatodos.com/category/noticias/">Últimas noticias</a></h2></div></div><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-54be18f elementor-widget elementor-widget-jw-posts" data-id="54be18f" dat